700050f-a.title: Bronx: 135th Street (East) - Brown Place
700050f-a.text:
East 135th Street, east from but not including Brown Place. The
buildings on the south side of the street are being demolished for the
construction of the approach to the Triborough Bridge.
May 11, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
